Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
save_cmd_file_limit(25.10)                          save_cmd_file_limit(25.10)

Name
       save_cmd_file_limit

Syntax
        save_cmd_file_limit <limit>

       Type: integer

       Default: 10

       The  saveDesign command saves the complete .cmd history across multiple
       sessions. The save_cmd_file_limit variable specifies  the  file  length
       limit  (in units of Mb) that is saved in the inn.cmd.gz file inside the
       save directory. If it is set to 0, the command history is not saved.

Related Information
